      "love": "Singles who have recently gone through a breakup will find it difficult to reconcile during this period, as the relationship has reached its breaking point. If the breakup hasn't been made official yet, clarity will come soon. Someone new entering your life may have recently endured a painful experience—heartbreak, job loss, or an accident. If you're interested in them, you must first become a healer.\n\nFor those in a relationship, if you haven't experienced an unexpected event like an accident, watch out for intense arguments. If the relationship has been struggling for a long time, it may be time to finally make a decision about your future together.",
